data.description: Make this house your home! This 3 bedroom 2 bath home is move-in ready. No HOA !! NO CDD !! Kitchen w/Tile floors & lots of cabinets and counter space. Tile floors throughout the living areas and carpet in the bedrooms. Living and Dining rooms open up to the patio. Big Screened patio overlooking a private little oasis. Fruit trees are Lychee, Banana, Mango, and Sugar apple, A/C is only 4 years old. Large 2-car garage.  Close to the turnpike/expressway. Short drive to Miami Beach or the Florida Keys.
